$$\begin{align*}
X(k) &amp;= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N - 1} {x(n){W_N^{nk}}} \quad \\
&amp;= \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r){W_N}^{2rk}} + \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r + 1){W_N}^{(2r + 1)k}} \\
&amp;= \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r)W_{N/2}^{rk}} + W_N^k\sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r + 1)W_{N/2}^{rk}} \\
&amp;= A(k) + W_N^k \cdot B(k)
\end{align*}$$

$$(\alpha, \beta) \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &amp;= \alpha + W \cdot \beta \\
\varphi_2 &amp;= \alpha - W \cdot \beta
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta = 
\begin{pmatrix} \varphi_1 \\ \varphi_2 \end{pmatrix}
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为编码颠倒的顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$分别奇偶向量组构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W = 
\begin{pmatrix}
&amp;W_n^0 &amp; &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; W_n^1 &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp;\ddots &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$"><h3>基本算法</h3><p><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG" display="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10.075ex" height="2.262ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -750 \begin{cases}
X(k) &amp;= A(k) + W_N^kB(k)\quad k = 0,1, \cdots ,\frac{N}{2} - 1 \\
X(k + \frac{N}{2}) &amp;= A(k) - W_N^kB(k)\quad k = 0,1, \cdots ,\frac{N}{2} - 1
\end{cases}
$$

$$\begin{align*}
X(k) &amp;= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n)\mathop W\nolimits_N^{nk} } + \sum\limits_{n = N/2}^{N - 1} {x(n)\mathop W\nolimits_N^{nk} } \\
&amp;= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n)\mathop W\nolimits_N^{nk} } + \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n + N/2)\mathop W\nolimits_N^{nk} } \mathop W\nolimits_N^{Nk/2} \\
&amp;= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {[x(n) + {{( - 1)}^k}x(n + N/2)]\;\mathop W\nolimits_N^{nk} } 
\end{align*}$$

$$\begin{pmatrix} \alpha\\ \beta\end{pmatrix} \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &amp;= \alpha + \beta \\
\varphi_2 &amp;= W \cdot (\alpha - \beta)
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta = (\varphi_1 , \varphi_2)
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为正常顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$分别奇偶向量组构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W = 
\begin{pmatrix}
&amp;W_n^0 &amp; &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; W_n^1 &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp;\ddots &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$"><h3>基本算法</h3><p><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG" display="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="9.359ex" height="5.43ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1450 4136.6 div.data-content:
## 时间抽取基2算法

$$\begin{align*}
X(k) &= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N - 1} {x(n){W_N^{nk}}} \quad \\
&= \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r){W_N}^{2rk}} + \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r + 1){W_N}^{(2r + 1)k}} \\
&= \sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r)W_{N/2}^{rk}} + W_N^k\sum\limits_{r = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(2r + 1)W_{N/2}^{rk}} \\
&= A(k) + W_N^k \cdot B(k)
\end{align*}$$

div.data-content:
### 基本算法

$$(\alpha, \beta) \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \alpha + W \cdot \beta \\
\varphi_2 &= \alpha - W \cdot \beta
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta =
\begin{pmatrix} \varphi_1 \\ \varphi_2 \end{pmatrix}
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为编码颠倒的顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$分别奇偶向量组构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W =
\begin{pmatrix}
&W_n^0 & & & \\
& & W_n^1 & \\
& & &\ddots & \\
& & & &W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$

, 分别奇偶向量组构成的矩阵
为维度与行维度相同的矩阵

考虑对称性

$$
\begin{cases}
X(k) &= A(k) + W_N^kB(k)\quad k = 0,1, \cdots ,\frac{N}{2} - 1 \\
X(k + \frac{N}{2}) &= A(k) - W_N^kB(k)\quad k = 0,1, \cdots ,\frac{N}{2} - 1
\end{cases}
$$

优化的地方在于, 在计算$X(k)$时, 保留$A(k)$与$W_N^k B(k)$可以轻易地计算出$X(k + \frac{N}{2})$

## 频率抽取基2算法

$$ egin{align*}
X(k) &= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n)\mathop W olimits_N^{nk} } + \sum\limits_{n = N/2}^{N - 1} {x(n)\mathop W olimits_N^{nk} } \
&= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n)\mathop W olimits_N^{nk} } + \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {x(n + N/2)\mathop W olimits_N^{nk} } \mathop W olimits_N^{Nk/2} \
&= \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{N/2 - 1} {[x(n) + {{( - 1)}^k}x(n + N/2)]\;\mathop W olimits_N^{nk} }
\end{align*}$$

div.data-content:
### 基本算法

$$\begin{pmatrix} \alpha\\ \beta\end{pmatrix} \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \alpha + \beta \\
\varphi_2 &= W \cdot (\alpha - \beta)
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta = (\varphi_1 , \varphi_2)
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为正常顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$分别奇偶向量组构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W =
\begin{pmatrix}
&W_n^0 & & & \\
& & W_n^1 & \\
& & &\ddots & \\
& & & &W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$
